{"tid":1562204,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[12/9 - 15/9] TGS 遊戲情報討論","createTime":"2019-09-12T02:25:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:18:28.000Z","uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"45adeaf983cbbb2175ead77d0e1f5d471db9ee4f","tid":1562204,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:25:22.000Z","msg":"<ins>PS4《Project Resistance》</ins><br />\n遊戲玩法正式公佈，新作以生化危機 作世界觀，並採用「1 vs 4」非對稱隊制玩法，加入系列熟悉敵人及場景，讓玩家合力體驗生存者之間的博弈！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn1-www.comingsoon.net/assets/uploads/2019/09/projectresistance.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1-www.comingsoon.net%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2Fprojectresistance.jpg&h=aa262052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lpLoVEWSZJ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlpLoVEWSZJ8&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=15021b88\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lpLoVEWSZJ8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>PS4《Final Fantasy VII Remake》</ins><br />\n主角Cloud與Aeris及Tifa美妙關係，更多熟悉臉孔現身，同時逐步掀開「神羅集團」陰謀詭計！<br />\nPS4《Final Fantasy VII Remake》中文版 2020年3月3日推出<br />\n預購進行中：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/FFVIIR_HKstore\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FFFVIIR_HKstore&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=971c0b25\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/FFVIIR_HKstore</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pGXs5eOgLP8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpGXs5eOgLP8&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=8d25f0b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pGXs5eOgLP8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>PS4《仁王２》</ins><br />\n新主角及「竹中直人」演出角色正式亮相！作為武士兼具超凡妖怪能力 + 人類血統的主角，帶領玩家穿越暗黑戰國時期，延續為國伏妖的使命！<br />\nPS4《仁王２》 預定2020年初推出︱更多介紹：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/nioh2_tgs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fnioh2_tgs&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=fa23ee0a\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/nioh2_tgs</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://asia.playstation.com/content/dam/pscom/japan-asia/latest-news/2019/heres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist/heres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist-image-06.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fpscom%2Fjapan-asia%2Flatest-news%2F2019%2Fheres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist%2Fheres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist-image-06.png&h=7bc2af00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://asia.playstation.com/content/dam/pscom/japan-asia/latest-news/2019/heres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist/heres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist-image-05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.playstation.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fpscom%2Fjapan-asia%2Flatest-news%2F2019%2Fheres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist%2Fheres-your-first-proper-look-at-nioh-2s-new-protagonist-image-05.png&h=f54da8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmCq0X6eXxE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHmCq0X6eXxE&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FXKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=abf1d89d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HmCq0X6eXxE</a>"},{"pid":"1321534f387a9cfb34464f5334a97654a0251dc4","tid":1562204,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:25:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold